"you are able to open your Plan or create a New Plan from scratch.      "
msgstr "仪表板是您的私人中心，其中包含您所有的计划以及与您共享的计划。您可以从仪表板打开您的计划或从头创建新计划。      "

# CTX-INTERPRETATION: This string appears as an instruction or tooltip in the
