msgstr ""
"        2) "
"其他卡片：每个卡片代表一个现有项目（自己的项目或其他用户共享的项目），可以访问和管理。点击卡片打开项目。点击卡片右上角的“三个点”可以执行重命名、共享、删除等操作。"
"      "

# CTX-INTERPRETATION: This string appears in the user interface of the
# Sim4Life.lite application, describing the availability and functionality of
# tutorial projects for users.
# CTX-VERSION: unknown
#: osparc/product/quickStart/s4llite/Dashboard.js
msgid ""
"        3) TUTORIALS: A set of pre-built read-only tutorial projects with "
"results is available to all Sim4Life.lite users. When a tutorial is "
"selected, a         copy is automatically created and added to the user’s "
"Projects tab. This new copy is editable and can be shared.      "
msgstr ""
"3) 教程：所有 Sim4Life.lite "
"用户都可以使用一组预构建的只读教程项目及其结果。当选择一个教程时，会自动创建一个副本并添加到用户的项目标签中。这个新副本是可编辑的并且可以共享。"
"      "

# CTX-INTERPRETATION: This string appears in the user manual or help section
# of the Sim4Life.lite application, guiding users on how to open an existing
# project.
# CTX-VERSION: unknown
#: osparc/product/quickStart/s4llite/Dashboard.js
msgid ""
"        4) To open an existing desktop project in Sim4Life.lite:         - "
"Click the + Start Sim4Life.lite button to create a new project.<br>        -"
" Click the menu and select “File Browser…”.<br>        - Click “Upload File”"
" for the .smash project and select the file from your desktop. Repeat the "
"same step, but this         time select “Upload Folder” and then select the "
"result folder from your desktop. Close the window<br>        - Click the "
"Menu again and click “Open” to select the file you just uploaded.<br>      "
msgstr ""
"4) 要在 Sim4Life.lite 中打开一个现有的桌面项目： - 点击 + 启动 Sim4Life.lite 按钮以创建一个新项目。<br> - "
"点击菜单并选择“文件浏览器…”。<br> - 点击“上传文件”以上传 .smash "
"项目文件，并从桌面选择文件。重复此步骤，但这次选择“上传文件夹”，然后从桌面选择结果文件夹。关闭窗口<br> - "
"再次点击菜单，然后点击“打开”以选择您刚刚上传的文件。<br>      "

# CTX-INTERPRETATION: This string likely appears as a section title or heading
