# outlining its features and limitations.
# CTX-VERSION: unknown
#: osparc/product/quickStart/s4llite/S4LLiteSpecs.js
msgid "Sim4Life.lite: Features and Limitations"
msgstr "Sim4Life.lite：功能和限制"

# CTX-INTERPRETATION: This string appears on the homepage of the Sim4Life.lite
# website, providing an overview of the platform's purpose and availability
# for students.
# CTX-VERSION: unknown
#: osparc/product/quickStart/s4llite/S4LLiteSpecs.js
msgid ""
"        Sim4Life.lite is a powerful web-based simulation platform that "
"allows you to model and analyze real-world phenomena and to         design "
"complex technical devices in a validated environment. Sim4Life.lite has been"
" created specifically for students to         facilitate their understanding"
" of computational modeling and simulations for various topics, ranging from "
"wireless communication         to medical applications. The access to "
"Sim4Life.lite is available free of charge to students enrolled at registered"
" universities.      "
msgstr ""
"Sim4Life.lite "
"是一个强大的基于网络的仿真平台，允许您在经过验证的环境中对现实世界现象进行建模和分析，并设计复杂的技术设备。Sim4Life.lite "
"专为学生设计，以帮助他们理解从无线通信到医疗应用等各种主题的计算建模和仿真。注册大学的在校学生可以免费访问 Sim4Life.lite。      "

# CTX-INTERPRETATION: This string appears as a feature list on the product
# page of the Sim4Life.lite scientific simulation application, highlighting
# its capabilities and components.
# CTX-VERSION: unknown
#: osparc/product/quickStart/s4llite/S4LLiteSpecs.js
msgid ""
"        <b>Sim4Life.lite offers</b><br>        - Framework (GUI, Modeling, "
"Postprocessing)<br>        - 3D modeling environment (based on the ACIS "
"toolkit) and CAD translators<br>        - Postprocessing and visualization "
"of the simulation results (2D and 3D viewers, 2D planar slice, volume "
"rendering, streamlines, surface fields on arbitrary 3D structures, radiation"
" and far-field data)<br>        - No restrictions on number of modeling "
"objects<br>        - Solvers & Tissue Models:<br>        &emsp;- P-EM-FDTD: "
"Electromagnetics Full-Wave Solver<br>        &emsp;- P-EM-QS: Quasi-Static "
"Electromagnetics Solver<br>        &emsp;- P-Thermal: Thermodynamic "
"Solver<br>        &emsp;- P-Acoustics: Acoustics Solver<br>        &emsp;- "
"T-Neuro: Neuronal Tissue Models<br>        - Computational anatomical model "
"Yoon-sun, the first Korean model of the IT’IS Virtual Population<br>        "
"- Material database<br>        - Python and Jupyter Notebook scripting      "
msgstr ""
"        <b>Sim4Life.lite 提供</b><br>        - 框架（GUI，建模，后处理）<br>        - 3D "
"建模环境（基于 ACIS 工具包）和 CAD 转换器<br>        - 模拟结果的后处理和可视化（2D 和 3D 查看器，2D "
"平面切片，体积渲染，流线，任意 3D 结构上的表面场，辐射和远场数据）<br>        - 对建模对象数量没有限制<br>        - "
"求解器和组织模型：<br>        &emsp;- P-EM-FDTD：电磁全波求解器<br>        &emsp;- P-EM-"
"QS：准静态电磁求解器<br>        &emsp;- P-Thermal：热力学求解器<br>        &emsp;- "
"P-Acoustics：声学求解器<br>        &emsp;- T-Neuro：神经组织模型<br>        - 计算解剖模型 "
"Yoon-sun，IT’IS 虚拟人口的第一个韩国模型<br>        - 材料数据库<br>        - Python 和 Jupyter"
" Notebook 脚本      "

# CTX-INTERPRETATION: This string appears in the limitations section of the
# user manual for a scientific simulation application, detailing the
# constraints and hardware requirements for running simulations.
# CTX-VERSION: unknown
#: osparc/product/quickStart/s4llite/S4LLiteSpecs.js
msgid ""
"        <b>Limitations</b><br>        The following limitations apply:<br>"
"        - Grid size of each simulation is limited to a maximum of <b>20 "
"million grid cells</b><br>        - High-Performance Computing is not "
"supported:<br>        &emsp;- GPU acceleration is not available<br>        "
"&emsp;- MPI multicore acceleration is not available<br>        - 3rd-party "
"tools are not available (e.g., MUSAIK, SYSSIM, IMAnalytics, etc…)<br>"
"        - Additional ViP models cannot be added<br>        - 30 minutes idle"
" time before logout<br>        - Hardware resource limits<br>        &emsp;-"
" 3 CPUs<br>        &emsp;- 3 GB of GPU RAM<br>        &emsp;- 5 GB disk "
"space<br>        &emsp;- 16 GB RAM<br>      "
msgstr ""
"        <b>限制</b><br>        以下限制适用：<br>        - "
"每个模拟的网格尺寸限制为最多<b>2000万个网格单元</b><br>        - 不支持高性能计算：<br>        &emsp;- "
"不支持GPU加速<br>        &emsp;- 不支持MPI多核加速<br>        - "
"不支持第三方工具（例如，MUSAIK、SYSSIM、IMAnalytics等）<br>        - 无法添加额外的ViP模型<br>"
"        - 空闲30分钟后自动注销<br>        - 硬件资源限制<br>        &emsp;- 3个CPU<br>"
"        &emsp;- 3 GB的GPU内存<br>        &emsp;- 5 GB的磁盘空间<br>        &emsp;- "
"16 GB的内存<br>      "

